I got coffee from this
morning. I could heat it up.

11:03.400 --> 11:04.595
Please.

11:11.200 --> 11:12.759
I'm gonna move these, okay?

11:12.840 --> 11:16.595
No! Actually, no, those are
my... No, no, put them down!

11:17.600 --> 11:18.670
No problem.

11:18.760 --> 11:20.194
I just got that organized.

11:23.440 --> 11:25.829
So, you collect these then?

11:25.920 --> 11:27.718
The beauty and travel mags?

11:27.800 --> 11:30.519
No. Not collect. (SIGHS)

11:30.600 --> 11:33.991
I gotta stay up with the latest
