I've seen the shows on TV.
Ironside and...

17:04.440 --> 17:07.353
This is all too important
to make mistakes here.

17:07.440 --> 17:12.037
So, get me a lawyer,
a good one,

17:12.119 --> 17:16.114
and if he says,
then I'll talk.

17:18.839 --> 17:22.276
No, Sonny, they just
called themselves plumbers,

17:22.359 --> 17:26.115
but what it was was a
special investigative unit

17:26.200 --> 17:27.598
inside the White House...

17:27.680 --> 17:28.829
BLUTH: Hey, Karl.

17:30.920 --> 17:33.275
Percy.
Got a customer for you.

17:33.360 --> 17:36.591
A client, I guess you...
Over at the station.

17:36.680 --> 17:38.796
Ed Blumquist?
Butcher's assistant?

17:38.880 --> 17:42.077
I guess he's mixed up
in all the craziness.

17:42.160 --> 17:44.390
You hear that, Sonny?

17:44.480 --> 17:48.792
There's a crisis at the highest
level, so who do they call?

17:48.920 --> 17:50.479
The best lawyer in town.

17:50.560 --> 17:52.597
Aren't you the only
lawyer in town, Karl?

17:52.680 --> 17:56.639
Yes, but that's because I
scared away all my... (CLANKING)

