Great Caesar's ghost.

17:59.240 --> 18:00.594
It would appear I'm
a little unstable...

18:00.680 --> 18:01.909
BLUTH: You okay there, Karl?

18:02.000 --> 18:03.673
Want me to tell Lou
you need a few hours?

18:03.760 --> 18:06.320
Fermez ton bouche, son.

18:06.400 --> 18:08.596
I am sound in mind and body,

18:08.680 --> 18:11.911
and ready to run circles
